---
import ImageCard from "./Image-Card.astro";
---

<section class="flex-col h-7/10 m-32">
  <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row my-12 mr-12">
    <div class="w-1/2">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold">Our Services</h2>
      <p class="text-xl">
        We offer a wide range of services to meet your needs.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-1/2">
      <div class="flex flex-row">
        <div class="flex-end">
          <p>
            In addition to house painting, we also offer painting services for
            commercial properties throughout the area. From offices and retail
            spaces to HOAs and other commercial buildings, we're experienced in
            working with a variety of businesses. We work within your schedule,
            and we are used to providing minimal disruption to our clients'
            day-to-day operations. By investing in a world-class paint job at
            your commercial property, you can uplift your brand, reduce
            downtime, and put your best foot forward for staff and customers
            alike
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-y-4 flex items-center mx-50">
    <ImageCard
      task="Interior Painting"
